 Trino Motion Pictures has premiered the official trailer for the forthcoming film “The Razz Guy” which sheds light on the reality that there are two sides to every man, directed by Udoka Oyeka. The film stars Nancy Isime, Lasisi Elenu, Broda Shaggi, MC Lively, Omotunde Adebowale-David (Lolo), Bucci Franklin, Olayemi Solade, Ireti Doyle, Norbert Young, Tina Mba, Ibrahim Suleiman, Shalewa Ashafa among others. Watch the trailer: 